tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MaintenanceRequests (
  request_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id INT NOT NULL,
  request_description TEXT,
  request_date DATE,
  resolution_description TEXT,
  resolution_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_requests (
    request_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    requester_name VARCHAR(50),
    request_date DATE,
    request_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_resolutions (
    resolution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    request_id INT,
    resolver_name VARCHAR(50),
    resolution_date DATE,
    resolution_description TEXT,
    resolution_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_requests (
  request_id INT,
  property_id INT,
  request_date DATE,
  description TEXT,
  status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE properties (
  property_id INT,
  property_name VARCHAR(50),
  address VARCHAR(100),
  city VARCHAR(50),
  state VARCHAR(2),
  zip_code VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE technicians (
  technician_id INT,
  first_name VARCHAR(30),
  last_name VARCHAR(30),
  email VARCHAR(50),
  phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE resolutions (
  resolution_id INT,
  request_id INT,
  resolution_date DATE,
  technician_id INT,
  notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_requests (
  request_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id INT,
  request_date DATE,
  description TEXT
)
